msItem.note:
The commentary is preceded by Thomas’s text (88v-106r). The
                        manuscript also contains a literal commentary on Thomas’s text (137r-170r;
                        inc.: insignis perypatetice veritatis interpres Doctor sanctus nedum
                           adultos provehi, verum in novitios afficiens erudire uberiores;
                        expl.: ipsa lux non eclipsalis, sed lucens eternaliter).
